languages.text: "///Иногда. Кого-то. Номос могут сделать многое. Не всегда знают, что и как. Не знали, что можем делать тишину до сейчас".

traits.locale_text: "///Иногда. Кого-то. Номос могут сделать многое. Не всегда знают, что и как. Не знали, что можем делать тишинудо сейчас".

languages.text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."
languages.original_text: "///Иногда. Кого-то. Номос могут сделать многое. Не всегда знают, что и как. Не знали, что можем делать тишину до сейчас".

languages.text: 「///時々。何人かの人々。ノモスはたくさんのことができます。何をどうするのか分からない時もあります。沈黙ができるのは今まで知りませんでした」
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: 「///時々。何人かの人々。ノモスはたくさんのことができます。何をどうするのか分からない時もあります。沈黙ができるのは今まで知りませんでした」

languages.text: ///有时可以，对某些人可以。诺莫斯可以做很多事情。我们并非总能知道是什么事情，或者该如何运作。直到刚才，我们才知道可以屏蔽他人的声音。”
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: ///有时可以，对某些人可以。诺莫斯可以做很多事情。我们并非总能知道是什么事情，或者该如何运作。直到刚才，我们才知道可以屏蔽他人的声音。”

languages.text: "///Manchmal. Manche Leute. Nomos können vieles tun. Wir wissen nicht immer was oder wie. Wir wussten bisher nicht, dass wir Schweigen erschaffen können."
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: "///Manchmal. Manche Leute. Nomos können vieles tun. Wir wissen nicht immer was oder wie. Wir wussten bisher nicht, dass wir Schweigen erschaffen können."

languages.text: « ///Parfois. Certaines personnes. Nous pouvons faire beaucoup de choses. Nous ne savons pas toujours quoi ni comment. Nous ne savions pas que nous pouvions imposer le silence jusqu'à maintenant. »
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: « ///Parfois. Certaines personnes. Nous pouvons faire beaucoup de choses. Nous ne savons pas toujours quoi ni comment. Nous ne savions pas que nous pouvions imposer le silence jusqu'à maintenant. »

languages.text: «///A veces. A algunas. Nomos podemos hacer muchas cosas. No siempre sabemos qué ni cómo. No sabíamos que podíamos hacer silencio hasta ahora».
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: «///A veces. A algunas. Nomos podemos hacer muchas cosas. No siempre sabemos qué ni cómo. No sabíamos que podíamos hacer silencio hasta ahora».

languages.text: "///Bazen. Bazı insanları. Nomos birçok şey yapabilir. Her zaman ne veya nasıl olduğunu bilmiyoruz. Sükûnet sağlayabileceğimizi şu ana dek bilmiyorduk."
languages.original_text: "///Sometimes. Some people. Nomos can do many things. We do not always know what or how. We did not know we could make silence until now."

traits.locale_text: "///Bazen. Bazı insanları. Nomos birçok şey yapabilir. Her zaman ne veya nasıl olduğunu bilmiyoruz. Sükûnet yapabileceğimizi şu ana dek bilmiyorduk."
